snippet: Ian Hobson began a 14-part survey of the complete chamber works for and with piano by Brahms on Tuesday at the DiMenna Center.
abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews concert of Brahms works performed by pianist Ian Hobson at DiMenna Center for Classical Music.
lead_paragraph: Ian Hobson began a 14-part survey of the complete chamber works for and with piano by Brahms on Tuesday at the DiMenna Center.

headline.seo: Ian Hobson Begins Brahms Recitals at DiMenna Center
headline.main: Brahms Rising: Echoes of a First Impression
